🌞 It’s sunbathing Sunday for me. What’s up for you?
.
.

#blaze#chocolatetoypoodle#toypoodle#chocolate#mydogisthebest#mypuppy#onlythebestforblaze#blaze#blazeandchocolates#puppiesanddreams#grooming#puppiesloversunite#cute#lovesleepingonmummy#friendly#sociable#everybodylovesblaze#sgdogs#singaporedogs#singapore#lampwork #lampworkbeads #poser #straitstimes #stayhome #stayathome #stayhomestaysafe #stayhomechallenge #stayhomesg #blazeturns4
We are hiding at home sleeping in aircon 😅
😍😍😍 show me your bikini tan later!!!😍😍😍💕💕💕💕
@spicey.icy i did! And hope it was great for u too!
Only in the morning we had sun😅 Hope you had a great Sunday dear Blaze!
@lil_misspriss12 would love to sunbathe with you 😁
Enjoy that sun. We are enjoying it here. ❤️
@buttercavapoo hope u had a lovely Sunday Buttercup 😘
Yay enjoy the sunbathing 🤗👍! We’re still sleeping; it’s Sunday morning for us ☺️
@biscuit.says yea!! I thot i saw someone that looked like you and i gave a shout out! 😁
“That’s a great view!! Saw any puppies walking outside and barked hello? 😄”
